headline: Wynn Resorts (WYNN) Stock Trades Up, Here Is Why
summary: Shares of luxury hotels and casino operator Wynn Resorts (NASDAQ:WYNN) jumped 3.4% in the afternoon session after Citigroup upgraded the company's stock to 'Buy' from 'Neutral' and significantly increased its price target.
